```plantuml
@startuml i5ting_stuq-koa
actor Developer
participant "Node.js Application" as App
participant "Koa.js Middleware" as Middleware
participant "Database" as DB
participant "HTTP Client" as Client

Developer -> App: Start Application
App -> Middleware: Initialize Middleware
Middleware -> Client: Accept HTTP Request
Client -> Middleware: Send Request Data
Middleware -> App: Process Request
App -> DB: Query/Modify Data
DB -> App: Return Data/Status
App -> Middleware: Prepare Response
Middleware -> Client: Send HTTP Response
Client -> Middleware: Acknowledge Response
@enduml
```